posting_body: ['BEDROOMS', '1 Bed', 'BATHROOMS', '1 Bath', 'SIZE', '518', 'VIRTUAL TOUR:', 'If the link does not appear below, the platform you are viewing this listing has blocked it from appearing.', 'Please contact us directly for a link to the virtual tour.', '3D Virtual Tour:  <URL>', 'Address: 1224 20th Ave #Front, San Francisco, CA 94122', 'Neighborhood: Inner Sunset', 'Bedrooms: 1', 'Bathrooms: 1', 'Kitchen: Stove, Fridge', 'Parking: Street', 'Pets: None, unless ESA or support animal.', 'Laundry:', 'None, Laundromat one block away', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Utilities included: None', 'Available: Now', 'FEATURES:', '• Large closets', '• Large living room', '• Hardwood floors', '• Highlights:', 'Located in the heart of Inner Sunset the 19th & Irving commercial corridor is just steps away with top-rated dining and cafes.', 'N-Judah Muni line is less than two blocks providing direct service to Downtown and the Financial District.', 'Or if work is at UCSF, take a stroll up Judah a couple blocks for an amazingly quick commute.', 'Escape to the seclusion and quiet of Golden Gate Park just across the street.', 'Your new home awaits you!!', 'REQUIREMENTS:', 'Credit: 650 Min', 'Income: 3x the Rent for aggregate household income', 'Guarantors Accepted', 'Security Deposit: 2X the rent (no deposit option for qualified renters <URL>)', 'Lease Terms: One year, month to month after', 'Application Fee: $50 per applicant', 'Resident Benefit Package included and required with all leases ($49.50/mo)']
